            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1614002927370-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> bulgur wheat </strong>to a pot with plenty of<strong> boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>(the same as you would for pasta)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot</p><p>Season the <strong>chicken breast portions</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a very generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> peppery chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1614002952577-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
