          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1614002952577-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk so they don't burn!</p><p>Transfer the <strong>toasted almonds</strong> to a bowl and return the pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1614002986990-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1614002986990-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1614002986990-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
