          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1614003001696-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>softened pepper &</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, most of the <strong>toasted almonds</strong> (save a few for garnish!) and the juice from 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon </strong>to a<strong> food processor</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then<strong> </strong>blitz until you have a coarse paste – this is your <strong>romesco sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1614003045929-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1614003045929-x400.jpg",
