            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1614003214475-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lemony bulgur wheat</strong> and <strong>cavolo nero</strong> with the <strong>sliced peppery chicken</strong> over the top</p><p>Dollop over the <strong>romesco sauce</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining toasted almonds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
